[[ja:ドラッグ_アンド_ドロップ]]
== OSX ==

Emacs 23 and 24 append files dragged over emacs' window to the current buffer.  If you want Emacs to open the file in a separate buffer like it does in older versions of emacs, use the following:

{{{
(define-key global-map [ns-drag-file] 'ns-find-file)
}}}

----
